# Testing Strategy (Seeded)

Goal: confidence without slowing the team down.

Prefer tests that are:

- deterministic
- fast enough for everyday use
- representative of real behaviour

---

## Recommended layers

- Unit tests: pure logic, no network/DB
- Integration tests: DB/network boundaries, API handlers, background jobs
- E2E tests: critical user journeys (only a few, stable)

